title: Paradise Worship - Only By Grace
description:
"Only By Grace" is the latest studio album from Paradise Worship released for 2008. It features 10 new tracks of bold, unashamed Praise and fresh, engaging Worship such as "Across the World"," Surrender" and title track "Only By Grace". Grace is the solution given to you by God to enable you to fix difficult relationships and situations. This album will inspire you to recognise that Grace is the invisible hand that opens impossible doors for you. Get ready to discover Him afresh as your FATHER.

Track Listing:
1. Across The World
2. My God & King
3. Mighty God
4. You Reign
5. Only By Grace
6. Can You Hear
7. The Heavens Declare
8. Surrender
9. You Lord
10 Wherever I Go
